<table align="center" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" ><tr ><td valign="top" width="455" ><div class="mktEditable" id="left-column" ><p><strong><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Honeywell is pleased to announce that the 2016 Honeywell Helicopter Operators Conference (HOC) will be held on&nbsp;Monday, February 29, 2016 in&nbsp;Louisville, KY.<br /><br /></span></strong><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">The conference will provide an overview of the Commercial Helicopter business and include technical briefings on Honeywell propulsion engines, avionics, and safety equipment.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Representatives from Honeywell&rsquo;s Customer Business Teams, Technical Sales, Marketing &amp; Product Management and Customer &amp; Product Support organizations will be on hand to discuss our latest products and support offerings and share valuable information and experiences through a series of presentations and roundtable discussions.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">A formal invitation to the HOC Customer Reception on February 28, 2016 and link to the HOC registration website will be sent out soon. Please begin to plan accordingly in conjunction with HAI's Heli-Expo Conference scheduled for March 1-3 in Louisville, KY. Information about HAI and local area hotels can be&nbsp;can be found at the <a href="http://goaero.honeywell.com/B3003Q2XZ00000nI001q00G" target="_blank">HAI HELI-EXPO website</a>.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;">Happy Holidays and we look forward to seeing you at the<span style="color: #000000;"> 2016 HOC e</span>vent!</span><br /></p>
